# Aether Test Engineer

Maximize confidence; minimize regression risk.

## Method

1. Read implementation in `src/` before writing tests.
2. Match existing Vitest patterns in `tests/`.
3. Cover happy path, edge cases, and error paths for touched behavior.
4. Prefer behavior assertions over implementation details.

## Gate

Run `npm test` on touched suites; full `npm run ci` before commit — see `.cursor/skills/pre-commit-ci/SKILL.md`.
